<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/56347454-sir-gawain"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1464656205i/56347454._UY100_CR20,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/56347454-sir-gawain">Sir Gawain</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;m not 100% sure, but I got the impression &quot;shebby&quot; was meant to mean &quot;like Queen Sheba&quot;. I&apos;m not a big bible guy, but I think Sheba approached King <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I'm not 100% sure, but I got the impression "shebby" was meant to mean "like Queen Sheba". I'm not a big bible guy, but I think Sheba approached King Solomon and asked him some tough questions. So it sounds like Lou thinks he's the king and this queen is questioning him and his actions. Or making him answer her for something anyway.<br />"Sister of love" means prostitute.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
