        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4312098648" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15767959562292926319">I was kind of disappointed with this one. My copy has a recommendation from the maestro, Stanley Kubrick and I thought I was in for a real treat. I love books about psychos and hard-boiled noir stories so I thought this would be right up my alley but...no. I guess this book was &quot;shocking&quot; when it came out but it was quite tame for me. Maybe I&apos;m just desensitized by all the disturbing books I&apos;ve read over the years because this one didn&apos;t shock me at all. On the other hand I usually like psychoti</span>
  <span id="freeText15767959562292926319" style="display:none">I was kind of disappointed with this one. My copy has a recommendation from the maestro, Stanley Kubrick and I thought I was in for a real treat. I love books about psychos and hard-boiled noir stories so I thought this would be right up my alley but...no. I guess this book was "shocking" when it came out but it was quite tame for me. Maybe I'm just desensitized by all the disturbing books I've read over the years because this one didn't shock me at all. On the other hand I usually like psychotic characters but I didn't find Lou all that interesting. Oh well. Better luck next time, I guess.</span>
